( 'email_settings', 'gmail_oauth', 'Gmail', 'WP Issues CRM can read and send mail through the Gmail API.  Gmail heavily filters incoming email, especially if forwarded, and so may not be suitable as a general purpose constituent inbox where responsiveness is a priority.', 3, 1, 0, '2000-01-01 01:01:01'),
