( 'email_settings', 'imap_to_wic_disqualifiers', 'Disqualifiers', 'List words that should identify a text block as NOT the address of the person sending the email -- typically, phrases from your name or address. Separate phrases with the pipe "|" character.  Other punctuation will be ignored.
